short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: GitHub file identification with GitHub Icon Changer Chrome ext. Get visually appealing icons and simplify your workflow.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Introducing the GitHub Icon Changer - a Google Chrome extension that revolutionizes the way you view and identify your repository files. No more struggling to figure out the file type just by looking at the file name. With this extension, you can easily identify the file type by simply glancing at the icon. Say goodbye to boring and generic file icons and hello to visually appealing and informative icons that help you work more efficiently on GitHub. Get the GitHub Icon Changer extension now and start personalizing your repository files.
